import React, {useState, useEffect} from 'react';


const pizzaForm = () => {


    return (

        <form>

            <label >
                Name:
            <input />
            </label>
            <label>
                Pizza Size:
            <input />
            </label>
            <label>
                Toppings:
            <input />
            </label>
            <label>
                Special instructions:
            <input />
            </label>
            <button >Order Now</button>

        </form>


    )


} 

export default pizzaForm;
